{"tid":371733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日係67暴動40週年！！！！","createTime":"2017-08-24T00:42:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T04:58:35.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bbf783d42c7bea47521f6244a475bda466435c92","tid":371733,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T00:42:53.000Z","msg":"以往就算是親建制的媒體，諸如亞洲電視，亦會在節目中提醒大家，1967年8月24日曾發生商台名嘴林彬被暗殺事件，而林生前曾嚴詞批評暴徒。<br />\n<br />\n1967年8月20日下午，暴徒在北角清華街擺放炸彈，炸死了8歲女童黃綺文及其2歲弟弟黃兆勳，引發社會公憤；林彬也在節目中痛罵暴徒喪盡天良、禽獸不如，但卻因此觸怒左派組織。據說，林彬當時連日接到恐嚇信，左派報紙更把林彬的名字改為「臨殯」，甚至公開聲稱要置之於死地。<br />\n<br />\n不幸的事終在1967年8月24日上午8時45分發生，當時林彬駕駛私家車途經何文田窩打老道山文運道，準備返回電台，其間被兩名偽裝成修路工人的兇徒攔截。兇手向車上潑汽油縱火，林彬全身著火，翌日傷重死亡，終年37歲，與其同車的堂弟林光海則昏迷留醫至8月30日不治。<br />\n<br />\n事發當天，有自稱「地下鋤奸突擊隊」司令部的組織發表公告，承認責任，指事件是「向林逆作出民族紀律的處分，嚴厲懲罰，以示儆戒」。而當年的「地下鋤奸突擊隊」，被普遍認為與暴徒有密切關係。<br />\n<br />\n儘管案件涉及兩條人命，但警方始終未能把暗殺林彬的暴徒繩之於法，林氏至今沉冤未雪。"},{"pid":"8274c3e9d70c3bf5b2a3c9dee1b320aafe6025b4","tid":371733,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T00:45:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/620177918009590/videos/1810060459021324/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F620177918009590%2Fvideos%2F1810060459021324%2F&d=ZXwma8W0dXeta1FKeUUtbwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=e6821cc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/620177918009590/videos/1810060459021324/</a>"},{"pid":"52f2e4fe0d9a2530ae5a6e5b21f9c16dae8e666b","tid":371733,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T00:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f806e8aeb8ac9feb27c52c44d5ec4acfa87b1b8b","tid":371733,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T01:02:21.000Z","msg":"數學家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d0164d048885ff89e9f49ba22eb9e95a565384d","tid":371733,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T01:36:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>數學家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n專登計錯架"},{"pid":"fc1fa3c06a443408de306f9cd90199ba455a1516","tid":371733,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T04:58:35.000Z","msg":"地下黨所為？"}]}